nodes.text: The G.O. was the name used by the Corellians to describe the government office complex located in Coronet. Along with the Corellian Assembly Building, the G.O. included bureau offices and the residence of the Head of State. Arranged in a classical garden style, formal gardens were interspersed among the buildings, and the entire complex was surrounded by Keben Park.
In 40 ABY Han Solo and a group of bounty hunters infiltrated the building and assassinated Head of State Thrackan Sal-Solo.
